Package: ukui-screensaver
Architecture: any
Depends: dbus-x11,
         ukui-desktop-common,
         ukui-screensaver-common (= ${source:Version}),
         ukui-session-manager,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
Recommends: ukui-power-manager,
Suggests: rss-glx,
          xscreensaver-data,
Breaks: ukui-screensaver-common,
Replaces: ukui-screensaver-common,
Description: UKUI screen saver and locker
 ukui-screensaver is a screen saver and locker that aims to have simple,
 sane and secure defaults, and be well integrated with the UKUI desktop.
 .
 It is designed to support, among other things:
 .
  * the ability to lock down configuration settings
  * translation into other languages
  * user switching

Package: ukui-screensaver-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
Breaks: ukui-screensaver,
Description: UKUI screen saver and locker (common files)
 ukui-screensaver is a screen saver and locker that aims to have simple,
 sane and secure defaults, and be well integrated with the UKUI desktop.
 .
 This package contains the architecture independent files.

